{"tid":220321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"癡肥遺體脂肪太多 火化時令火勢變猛釀火災","createTime":"2017-04-28T00:58:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T02:28:18.000Z","uid":18348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"47a0e584500a964abc8cc514dd09200e4cfa233c","tid":220321,"uid":18348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T00:58:15.000Z","msg":"美國俄亥俄州一間殯儀館發生離奇意外，職員火化一具癡肥遺體時，火勢突然變猛，更擴散至火化爐外釀成火警；幸事件中無人受傷，火勢亦未波及其他屍體。<br />\n<br />\n大火發生在周二晚，殯儀館負責人卡奇恩（Don Catchen）指，火化期間火勢變得強勁，令大火擴散至火化爐外，並燒著一個火化箱，「那具遺體屬癡肥，火化過程明顯比一般的更熱」。<br />\n<br />\n消防員表示幸火葬場做足防火措施，成功阻止火勢蔓延，事件沒人受傷，亦未有波及其他屍體。<br />\n<br />\n業內人士指火化癡肥遺體有危險，是因為會出現俗稱「油脂火」，維珍尼亞州2014年火化一具500磅遺體時亦曾發生火警；奧地利在2012年火化一具440磅的女屍時亦引發火燭，令消防員「覆蓋着一層烏黑油脂」。<br />\n<br />\n英國《都巿報》/《每日鏡報》"},{"pid":"7b1e50d26cd23b18eb9d640ee531e355e200be02","tid":220321,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T00:59:23.000Z","msg":"肥就是罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19bbdaee446164fb331c8d506072b66e7921ec09","tid":220321,"uid":863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T01:00:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4127ac549547b4b08a5616ff8e919ada28945c8","tid":220321,"uid":61545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T01:00:55.000Z","msg":"攞嚟發電都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3865da6a40b4d56411621c26e628f3983e95564f","tid":220321,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T01:00:59.000Z","msg":"諗起董卓"},{"pid":"382dc124c4e357a259300231bb3e6dbbcb22f060","tid":220321,"uid":18348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T01:01:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170428&amp;guid=56621060&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170428%26guid%3D56621060%26category_guid%3